## âš™ï¸ Configuration
Edit these variables at the top of `auto_backup.py`:

```python
SOURCE_DIR = r"C:\path\to\source"    # Folder you want to back up
BACKUP_DIR = r"C:\path\to\backup"    # Destination folder for backups
MAX_BACKUPS = 5                      # Max backups to keep
BACKUP_FORMAT = "zip"                # "zip" or "tar.gz"

## ğŸš€ Usage
python auto_backup.py

## Example Output
[+] Creating zip backup: C:\path\to\backup\backup_2025-09-06_14-30-00.zip
[+] Backup created successfully.
[!] Removing 1 old backup(s).
[x] Removed C:\path\to\backup\backup_2025-09-04_10-00-00.zip

